---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import EstimateModal from '../components/EstimateModal.astro';

const title = 'Customer Reviews - Stump Grinding Jacksonville FL | Stumpmasters Jax';
const description = 'Read real customer reviews for Stumpmasters Jax stump grinding and tree removal services in Jacksonville, FL. See why we have a 5-star rating on Google!';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  <Breadcrumbs items={[
    { label: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { label: 'Reviews' }
  ]} />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Reviews Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative bg-black py-12 px-4 border-b-4 border-brand-yellow">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-yellow mb-4">
          Customer Reviews
        </h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-brand-yellow mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        
        <!-- Google Rating Summary -->
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="flex gap-1">
            {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-yellow fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
              </svg>
            ))}
          </div>
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">5.0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6">Based on 6 Google reviews</p>
        <a 
          href="https://www.google.com/search?q=stumpmasters+jax" 
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-black font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 transition"
          onclick="trackEvent('Click', { category: 'Reviews', label: 'View Google Reviews Page' })"
        >
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M12.48 10.92v3.28h7.84c-.24 1.84-.853 3.187-1.787 4.133-1.147 1.147-2.933 2.4-6.053 2.4-4.827 0-8.6-3.893-8.6-8.72s3.773-8.72 8.6-8.72c2.6 0 4.507 1.027 5.907 2.347l2.307-2.307C18.747 1.44 16.133 0 12.48 0 5.867 0 .307 5.387.307 12s5.56 12 12.173 12c3.573 0 6.267-1.173 8.373-3.36 2.16-2.16 2.84-5.213 2.84-7.667 0-.76-.053-1.467-.173-2.053H12.48z"/>
          </svg>
          Read All Reviews on Google
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Reviews Content -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-700">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 text-center mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          See what our customers have to say about our stump grinding and tree removal services in Jacksonville, FL
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Review 1 - Mack Oyler -->
          <div class="bg-black border-2 border-brand-yellow rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Mack O.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">DEC 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-1">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                  </svg>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Stumpmasters Jax did an outstanding job from start to finish. They were fast, courteous, and incredibly professional. You can tell right away that they know their craft. Everything was explained clearly, communication was great, and the whole process was handled smoothly.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              It was honestly a breath of fresh air having a U.S. veteran take care of the work. Not only did it feel good supporting a veteran-owned business, but as a fellow veteran, I really appreciated the level of thoroughness and pride they put into the job. Nothing was rushed, nothing was left half-done, and I never had to worry about what the final result would look like.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Friendly, knowledgeable, and genuinely great with customersâ€¦ couldn't ask for anything more. I was very impressed and would recommend Stumpmasters Jax to anyone needing stump grinding or similar services. Highly worth it.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Review 2 - Shannon Lowery -->
          <div class="bg-black border-2 border-brand-yellow rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Shannon L.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">NOV 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-1">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                  </svg>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              I had an amazing experience with this stump removal service! They were fast, professional, and super thorough. The crew showed up on time, explained everything clearly, and had the stump gone before I knew it. They cleaned up the entire area afterward, leaving my yard looking better than before.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              The price was fair, the communication was great, and the quality of their work speaks for itself. If you need stump grinding or removal done right, I highly recommend them. I'll definitely be using them again for any future yard projects!
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Review 3 - Stela Fiku -->
          <div class="bg-black border-2 border-brand-yellow rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Stela F.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">NOV 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-1">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                  </svg>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Awesome customer service! I had a million questions which I'm sure was super annoying, but they were SO patient and helpful. Pricing was more than fair and their work was impeccable!
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Review 4 - Senida Kuljancic -->
          <div class="bg-black border-2 border-brand-yellow rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Senida K.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">DEC 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-1">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                  </svg>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Stumpmasters is incredible! I'm recommending them to everyone I know. Quick, informative, and excellent at communicating!
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Seriously, save yourself time and money and give them a call.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Review 5 - William Voellmecke -->
          <div class="bg-black border-2 border-brand-yellow rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">William V.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">DEC 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-1">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                  </svg>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Professional and reasonably priced. Was able to fit me in same day and did a fantastic job! Highly recommend.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Review 6 - Tamara Bukonjic -->
          <div class="bg-black border-2 border-brand-yellow rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Tamara B.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">NOV 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-1">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                  </svg>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              They were super quick to respond and fairly priced. Great customer service!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="mt-16 bg-black border-4 border-brand-yellow rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-yellow mb-4">
            Ready to Join Our Happy Customers?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Experience the same professional service that earned us these 5-star reviews!
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a 
              href="tel:+19044082450"
              class="px-8 py-3 bg-brand-yellow text-black text-lg font-bold rounded hover:bg-yellow-400 transition"
              onclick="trackEvent('Click', { category: 'Contact', label: 'Reviews Page CTA Phone' })"
            >
              ðŸ“ž Call 904-408-2450
            </a>
            <button 
              data-open-estimate-modal
              class="px-8 py-3 bg-gray-700 text-white text-lg font-bold rounded hover:bg-gray-600 transition border-2 border-brand-yellow"
            >
              Request Free Estimate
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
